comments.text:
Against recent Nightly on WinXP (thus D3D9 at best) disabling the box-shadow Style in

body {
  background-attachment: fixed;
  background-color: rgb(8, 181, 251);
  padding: 60px 0pt;
  color: rgb(255, 255, 255);
  text-shadow: 0pt 1px 2px
    rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
  text-rendering: optimizelegibility;
  background-repeat: repeat-x;
  background-image: -moz-linear-gradient(rgb(97, 48, 150),
    rgb(8, 181, 251));
  box-shadow: 0pt 50px 200px
    rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2) inset;
}

helps. Maybe this is equally to Usage of D3D10/D2D on Win7.

